<head>
  <title>Setting Up Your Python Development Environment</title>
</head>

<body>
<h1>Setting Up Your Python Development Environment</h1>

<h2>bash</h2>

<pre class='shell'>
$ mkdir bin lib
$ mkdir lib/python
</pre>

<pre class='shell'>
PATH=$HOME/bin:$PATH
PYTHONPATH=$HOME/lib/python
EDITOR=vi

export PATH PYTHONPATH EDITOR
</pre>


<h2>vim</h2>

<pre class='shell'>
syntax enable
filetype indent on
set et
set sw=4
set smarttab
map &lt;f2&gt; :w\|!python %&lt;cr&gt;
</pre>

</body>
</html>
